content.text:
Under clause 3 of rule XII,

       145. The SPEAKER presented a memorial of the Senate of the 
     State of Michigan, relative to Senate Resolution No. 103, 
     congratulating the government and people of the Republic of 
     China (Taiwan) on their 106th National Day on October 10, 
     2017; which was referred to the Committee on Foreign Affairs.
